## MapView.nativeWebglAntialiasEnabled property

Returns `true` if the native WebGL antialiasing is enabled.

 `true` for `pixelRatio` &lt; `2.0`<!-- -->, `false` otherwise.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
get nativeWebglAntialiasEnabled(): boolean;
```
